### Jamf Protect

This Kibana dashboard features a range of visualizations highlighting key events and the most recent alerts. It serves as a customizable template, allowing adjustments to meet specific organizational needs.

query.query: (observer.product : "Jamf Protect" and event.module : "Alerts" and event.severity : 1) or (observer.product :"Jamf Protect" and event.module :"Threat Events Stream" and event.severity : 4)
(observer.product : "Jamf Protect" and event.module : "Alerts" and event.severity : 2) or (observer.product :"Jamf Protect" and event.module :"Threat Events Stream" and event.severity : 6)
(observer.product : "Jamf Protect" and event.module : "Alerts" and event.severity : 3) or (observer.product :"Jamf Protect" and event.module :"Threat Events Stream" and event.severity >= 8)

panelsJSON.title: Top processes related to detection and hostname
Top 10 process shahex values by process executable

query.query: observer.product : "Jamf Protect" and event.module : "Alerts" and NOT process.code_signature.signing_id:com.apple.*

embeddableConfig.description: Apple's signed binaries are not bound to an TeamID.

panelsJSON.title: Top process Signing Information by TeamID
